---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Card from "../components/Card.astro"
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import Logo from "components/Logo.astro";
import Fluff from "components/Fluff.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home">
	<div id="hero">
		<div>
			<img src="/big-logo.png" width="325" height="100" />
			<h1>An elegant design.</h1>
		</div>
		<Fluff />
	</div>

	<p>Dreen is a graceful design language oriented to blog themes, personal websites, and small websites, etc.</p>
	<p><strong>It's not for big and complicated web applications!</strong></p><br>

	<p>This design is still being developed; if you love the face of it, I hope I can see you on <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/zihan-ch/dreen">the Github repo of Dreen.</a></p>
</Layout>

<style>
	#hero {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-bottom: 10%;
	}
	
	#big-logo {
		
	}

	#big-logo * {
		position: relative;
	}

	p {
		font-size: 1.35em;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}
</style>